# AGENTS.md and master commands

- Read and follow **`AGENTS.md`** at the **repository root** (same directory as `app/`, `docs/`, etc.).
- Treat the **Master commands** section there as **binding** project directives. If it conflicts with a vaguer suggestion, **Master commands win**.
